{"tid":394994,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Jump 50周年展，原哲夫向荒木飛呂彥請教養生","createTime":"2017-09-10T12:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T01:01:57.000Z","uid":64191,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e3575a3225c7ab6205945d23ec6919ee43bb85d","tid":394994,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:26:42.000Z","msg":"近排Jump雜誌舉辦創刊50周年展，其中有原哲夫（北斗之拳作者）與荒木飛呂彥（JOJO奇妙冒險作者）進行對談節目<br />\n<br />\n原哲夫向荒木問：點解你大我一歲，但睇落比我後生<br />\n<br />\n荒木飛呂彥就回應：我以前鍾意潛水，但有次遇溺後就改玩行山<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，荒木飛呂彥響創作Jojo之前被編輯邀請，用公帑到埃及旅行，返國後就正式創作《Jojo奇妙冒險》<br />\n<br />\n所以話，當時埃及發生左咩事⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/bggbPgz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbggbPgz.jpg&h=65e39aab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n附圖：荒木飛呂彥、原哲夫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://natalie.mu/comic/news/248100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnatalie.mu%2Fcomic%2Fnews%2F248100&d=pHA8xSnmiKajWaFOQZ69K8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0163baeb\" target=\"_blank\">http://natalie.mu/comic/news/248100</a><br />\n<br />\n原文網址"},{"pid":"14389d14fbba5d4a6e57091ea5a0d0324967f8e0","tid":394994,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"將時間停止嘅男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9972bd6dbc6e917f5b9cd0fe6c5807fcc7f99bb5","tid":394994,"uid":18818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"荒木飛呂彥就回應：人類的力量是很有限的..."},{"pid":"2707a1afdf2755ff459822360a35a4eaea18fe4a","tid":394994,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:41:39.000Z","msg":"石像鬼&hellip;"},{"pid":"f754285900dba00bf32003c4a96aa10c35d03518","tid":394994,"uid":39221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"柱男"},{"pid":"c9e83e951861b24232afa362c3771bbcd33ab3bf","tid":394994,"uid":70997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":